{"tid":569631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【媽媽起身啦】小犀牛肚餓想吃奶 不知媽媽已遭獵殺","createTime":"2018-02-23T01:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T04:44:47.000Z","uid":48083,"like":137,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"c0572a31fa07ed4dd12dd8a8818fff1b55724f43","tid":569631,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/091936_a2c38ea799aa5132cdb4eb3f5ea91bad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F091936_a2c38ea799aa5132cdb4eb3f5ea91bad.png&h=54ae70cf&s={SIZE}\" />南非一個國家公園近日上演悲劇，一隻小犀牛試圖吃媽媽的奶，卻不知犀牛媽媽已被偷獵者殺害。<br />\n<br />\n片段顯示，肚餓的犀牛崽在媽媽身邊徘徊，嘗試探頭到媽媽身下吃奶，但媽媽毫無反應。小犀牛吃奶不成，彷彿以為媽媽只是睡着了，還行到媽媽耳邊像是要叫醒牠似的。<br />\n<br />\n不過，那隻犀牛媽媽永遠也不能餵哺小犀牛了，因為牠已被偷獵者殺掉並鋸去犀牛角。<br />\n<br />\n那隻犀牛媽媽已是該公園四周內第11隻被獵殺的犀牛。犀牛角值錢，黑市價高達11萬港元，成為偷獵者覬覦對象。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180222/57860189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180222%2F57860189&d=46fcM0%2BWrLG%2F%2F9vNxla2UC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=844dec62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180222%2F57860189&h=27968c9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180222/57860189</a>"},{"pid":"80d9e967bd84e0b78fa4b922cf0952b5273fa26c","tid":569631,"uid":52215,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd9717299d904a035af6e79f70ad7a26d634664","tid":569631,"uid":35430,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo