ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:19:52.000Z","msg":"The investigation exposed WeChat and Facebook accounts used to advertise banned wildlife parts and 17 Chinese bank accounts used by traffickers to take payment from Chinese customers.<br />\n<br />\nUndercover video footage gathered by the group shows a young woman sitting behind a counter in a Nhi Khe shop, as customers from China &ndash; the village's main market &ndash; handle bracelets and necklaces made of rhino horn."},{"pid":"83a3a56ef327974688fd34f9e67f4c9bdadc3d25","tid":569631,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3e62aac44c04e71d736dc3be9489552e66455eb","tid":569631,"uid":18241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f98ba9d13974e220fda9b958025eb5cf65a57ea1","tid":569631,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"11c762cc7bb1ad1020a1ae42b7867dde29fa2878","tid":569631,"uid":4934,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:55:56.000Z","msg":"你戇鳩㗎？ 拎偷獵者同食肉嘅人比較<br />\n傻撚咗？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T04:56:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:10:41.000Z","msg":"其實好大分別"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:20:21.000Z","msg":"前者只是個人興趣 玩樂<br />\n後者為生物本能 生物生存的問題"},{"pid":"d81951563ce62c5ef018f22bb7fb109f381332bb","tid":569631,"uid":169468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:22:13.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到張相好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3985488836f5c67aa50ed988fcbce96c27fd96e1","tid":569631,"uid":38172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:23:20.000Z","msg":"諗起MON HUNT, 要優角, 入場爆完角就走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0af4d1038e737beff86f1e206bacc3b6cc080e","tid":569631,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e04cbe326648306d730fb732924c898fd8b5e48","tid":569631,"uid":26451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:24:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6395074286b565bef7ece2efc3d2e1184f666a0d","tid":569631,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d44f4e34916789a440b23e54666c72bca1d90ed","tid":569631,"uid":160916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d60002e5497b9c2579175df840fce974a4f9d730","tid":569631,"uid":20072,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T03:07:28.000Z","msg":"如果細細個就割左隻角得唔得, 唔怕比人HUNT<br />\n但會唔會無左搵食能力?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:25:06.000Z","msg":"睇電視見過類似嘅做法防偷獵者, 不過唔記得係咪犀牛"},{"pid":"c58737615915234e1dcecfa2a89c902762fb3fe0","tid":569631,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:25:29.000Z","msg":"史料[編輯]<br />\n《晉書》講述晉朝名仕溫嶠在武昌周旋，於牛渚磯見水深難測，而世代也有說水下多怪物，溫嶠便將犀牛角燃燒照明；不久，在照進水中的火光裡，隱約出現一些水中生物[1]，形狀怪異，甚至看到有穿赤衣、乘馬車的人出現。當晚，溫嶠在夢中看到有人甚為厭惡地對他說：「我與先生人鬼不同路，為何照我呢？」。[2]而未知是否真的因靈界作祟，有齒疾的溫嶠在拔牙後，因而中風，不久便逝世了。<br />\n<br />\n所以相傳燃點犀牛角，可目睹靈界異象。而「犀照」一詞後來亦用來比喻洞燭幽微，明察事理之意。"},{"pid":"630f118a9b08da0e5bf68c1ab4ce8a1749eab3a0","tid":569631,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:25:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8ac517f41aa68040e5cc4eb5e4e680e160ae950","tid":569631,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中醫萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>召喚會員名稱上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://www.latimes.com/world/africa/la-fg-vietnam-rhino-trafficking-20160926-snap-story.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fworld%2Fafrica%2Fla-fg-vietnam-rhino-trafficking-20160926-snap-story.html&d=46fcM0%2BWrLG%2F%2F9vNxla2UC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=0f4cec08\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.latimes.com/world/africa/la-fg-vietnam-rhino-trafficking-20160926-snap-story.html</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>The investigation exposed WeChat and Facebook accounts used to advertise banned wildlife parts and 17 Chinese bank accounts used by traffickers to take payment from Chinese customers.<br />\n<br />\nUndercover video footage gathered by the group shows a young woman sitting behind a counter in a Nhi Khe shop, as customers from China &ndash; the village's main market &ndash; handle <span style=\"color: red;\">bracelets and necklaces</span> made of rhino horn.</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fb518d17c48b182ebc6388e3f9a1ef5840694526","tid":569631,"uid":48259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:28:09.000Z","msg":"動物都有性過人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f647888608bf19d8903b5e1c49df83bc18829a2","tid":569631,"uid":71376,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食肉既都無資格出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>你戇鳩㗎？ 拎偷獵者同食肉嘅人比較<br />\n傻撚咗？</blockquote>其實冇分別</blockquote>都係為左私利<br />\n一個係果腹<br />\n一個係金錢<br />\n<br />\n金錢到最後都係果腹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以下單純係假設<br />\n<br />\n我會視食肉為某程度上既一種必需品，食肉時我會心存感激<br />\n而且我都會節制，唔會食得太多<br />\n屠宰時人類都會諗辦法設計減少動物既痛苦<br />\n但係呢d都唔係偷獵者會考慮既問題<br />\n佢地只會諗點樣殺最多既犀牛，搵最多既錢<br />\n<br />\n咁樣足唔足以將食肉者同偷獵者作出區分？"},{"pid":"0316994d4cb67e5406fe464884cd4ec9043215e9","tid":569631,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"